Sikkim quake India ' s fourth in September Last Updated : Sunday , September 18 , 2011 , 20 : 51 1620 9 Tweet Tags : India quake , Sikkim quake , Northeast New Delhi : The 6 . 8 - magnitude earthquake in India ' s Sikkim state on Sunday evening was the fourth tremor reported in the country in September so far , according to the India Meteorological Department ( IMD ).